# Module Federation Standards (Rspack)

## Required plugin
Use:
- `@module-federation/enhanced/rspack` -> `ModuleFederationPlugin`



## Mandatory shared singletons (all apps)
- `react`
- `react-dom`
- `@tanstack/react-query`
- `@tanstack/react-router`


All must be configured as:
- singleton: true
- requiredVersion: false (versions enforced via root overrides)

## Exposes
- platform:
  - ./AppProviders
  - ./queryClient
  - ./account
- domain remotes:
  - ./routes

## Ports
- shell: 3000
- platform: 3001
- traffic: 3002
- reports: 3003
- admin: 3004

## Output / DevServer
- `output.publicPath = "auto"`
- `devServer.historyApiFallback = true`
